TITLE DataQualityInvariants2026v1
ALNSPECHASHHEX 0x????????????????        # fill via hex-stamping
SCHEMANAME ecosafety.dataquality.invariants.2026v1
CATEGORY ECOSAFETY
DESCRIPTION Uncertainty monotonicity invariants for rcalib and rsigma under KER.

PARTICLE DataQualityInvariants2026v1
  ROLE       INVARIANT
  VERSIONTAG v1
  LYAPCHANNEL dataquality

  FIELD invariant_id STRING META
    DESCRIPTION Invariant identifier.

  FIELD coord_id     STRING META
    DESCRIPTION Risk coordinate, e.g., rcalib, rsigma.

  FIELD apply_lanes  STRING META
    DESCRIPTION Comma-separated lanes where this invariant applies, e.g., "RESEARCH,EXPPROD,PROD".

  FIELD require_K_non_increase BOOL META
    DESCRIPTION If TRUE, K_next must be <= K_prev when coord worsens.

  FIELD require_E_non_increase BOOL META
    DESCRIPTION If TRUE, E_next must be <= E_prev when coord worsens.

  FIELD require_R_non_decrease BOOL META
    DESCRIPTION If TRUE, R_next must be >= R_prev when coord worsens.

  FIELD ownerdid     STRING META
    DESCRIPTION Bostrom DID owning this invariant spec.

  FIELD evidencehex  STRING META
    DESCRIPTION Hex-encoded evidence chain for this invariant definition.

  FIELD signinghex   STRING META
    DESCRIPTION Hex-encoded signature bound to ownerdid.

  FIELD issued_utc   DATETIME META
    DESCRIPTION Timestamp when this invariant was issued.

ENDPARTICLE
